Boost C++ Libraries Ubuntu 18

Install Boost Development Libraries

    sudo apt update
    sudo apt install -y libboost-all-dev

Verify Installation and Version

    dpkg -l | grep boost

The Boost headers are typically installed in 

/usr/include/boost, and 

the libraries are in /usr/lib.

--------------------------------------------

In (Manjaro/Arch) Linux -->

    sudo pacman -S boost

 List Installed Boost Files

    pacman -Ql boost | grep include
    pacman -Ql boost | grep lib

--------------------------------------------
